# Todo MD

`.ai/protocols/TODO_MD_AGENT_PROTOCOL.md` — read and follow it whenever you touch `.ai/todo/` or the user asks about tasks / Todo MD. That file is the only maintained copy; do not restate its rules elsewhere. **Assistants never delete or remove todo lines** in the three `.ai/todo/*.md` files (human-only removals).
